<plot>A six-part documentary series about presenting Shakespeare today. The episode titles highlight the broader themes in Shakespeare, while the contents focus down on a particular play, or even scene, highlighting that theme. King Lear, A Midsummers Night's Dream, Henry V, As You Like It, and Measure for Measure are featured.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?114074</url></doc>
